Name: Upload Job

Description:
  The user will be able to upload a job description to the app
  
Players: user, admin, database
  
Preconditions: Logged in succesfully 

Basic flow:
  1) Select menu
  2) The menu opens up
  3) Selecting the jobs page
  4) Job window opens up
  5) Select "upload Job"
  6) Upload job window opens up
  7) Insert job descriptions
  8) Click on upload job
  
Alternate flow:
  -
  
Exception flow:
  If job description wasent filled in properly, there will be a message that pops up and a red sign around relevent boxes

Post conditions:
The job appears on the jobs page
